{"tid":800692,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"莫迪歷當選西甲最差收購","createTime":"2018-08-31T05:36:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T11:21:54.000Z","uid":31314,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8f15cab227dfbc2a091fd03cee9c49c8afa9b57c","tid":800692,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T05:36:54.000Z","msg":"《馬卡報》讀者選出莫迪歷和桑治成為今季西甲最差收購。 <br />\n<br />\n皇家馬德里中場莫迪歷（Luka Modric）和巴塞隆拿中場桑治，分別被《馬卡報》讀者選為今季最差的收購，得票分別為32.2%。莫迪歷去年夏天由熱刺加盟皇馬，桑治則由阿仙奴加盟巴塞，可惜兩人均未能成為球隊常規主力，也證明即使是英超兵也不易在西甲立足。 <br />\n<br />\n莫迪歷季初曾經有過不俗的表現，但面對防中主將沙比阿朗素和進攻中場奧斯爾的競爭，他很快就失去正選地位，至今合共上陣19次、8次踢足全場，比賽時間為717分鐘，但只有1個入球。 <br />\n<br />\n桑治是防守中場出身，但大部分比賽都打中堅，只拿到可憐的7次上陣機會。"},{"pid":"5b23b88e5cd46d8a449e5bfb1b4a1e45c1582b06","tid":800692,"uid":153600,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T05:38:16.000Z","msg":"Song真係收左皮 la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係Modric...... 想笑撚死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22eb30dd791212fe374c4de68e12e12693e821e1","tid":800692,"uid":13395,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5b23b88e5cd46d8a449e5bfb1b4a1e45c1582b06","tid":800692,"uid":153600,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T05:38:16.000Z","msg":"Song真係收左皮 la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n